<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/1999-07-20.8.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-99/wa0720.htm#179">Food</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/1999-07-20.8.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80203" speakername="Irene McGugan (North-East Scotland) (SNP)" spid="S1W-179" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-99/wa0720.htm#179">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive when it envisages the Food Standards Agency being operational in Scotland.</p>

</ques>


